txt.en: War-hounds and their Corsair handlers can be found at Abedec's Watch in southern Belfalas.\n\nYou should battle the war-hounds and the Corsairs who act as their brutal masters.

War-hounds and their Corsair handlers prowl throughout Abedec's Watch on the coast of Belfalas, concealed amongst some old Gondorian ruins.\n\nYou should battle the war-hounds and the Corsairs who act as their brutal masters.
